@startuml auto-detection
!theme plain

actor User
participant "Geofence" as Geo
participant "BroadcastReceiver" as Receiver
participant "Database" as DB

User -> Geo: Arrives at office
Geo -> Receiver: ENTER event
Receiver -> DB: Save entry time
Receiver -> User: Show "Arrived" notification

...User works...

User -> Geo: Leaves office
Geo -> Receiver: EXIT event
Receiver -> DB: Save exit time
Receiver -> Receiver: Calculate hours
Receiver -> DB: Save daily entry
Receiver -> User: Show "Left - 9h" notification

@enduml

